object.customQuery:
SELECT 
  policy_source_system_id,
  'Policy' AS policy_cmm_container,
  policy_number, 
  policy_module_number,
  line_of_business,
  policy_effective_date,
  risk_state,
  insured_name,
  customer_number,
  overall_rule_pass_fail_indicator,
  GETDATE()::date AS task_work_date,
  'UnderwritingPersonalLines' AS task_original_owner,
  'Group' AS task_original_owner_code,
  'UnderwritingPersonalLines' AS task_current_owner,
  'Group' AS task_current_owner_code,
  1 AS task_priority,
'- ' || rule_name || ': ' || condition_column_name_left || COALESCE(calculation_operator || COALESCE(condition_column_name_right 
|| calculation_constant_value,'') ,'') || ' - ' || final_value AS task_text,
  rule_type,
  rule_row_pass_fail_indicator
FROM $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data
WHERE 
stp_validated_data_loaded_to_api_table_status = 'Load to API table pending'
AND overall_rule_pass_fail_indicator = 'FAIL'
AND rule_row_pass_fail_indicator = 'FAIL'
ORDER BY policy_source_system_id, rule_id, condition_order_number, straight_through_processing_rule_row_id;

fields.name: o_stp_api_data_row_md5checksum
fields.expression:
MD5('policy_source_system_id' || to_char(policy_source_system_id) ||
'policy_number' || policy_number ||
'policy_module_number' || policy_module_number ||
'line_of_business'|| line_of_business ||
'policy_effective_date'|| to_char(policy_effective_date) ||
'risk_state'||risk_state ||
'insured_name' || insured_name ||
'customer_number' ||customer_number ||
'overall_rule_pass_fail_indicator' || overall_rule_pass_fail_indicator ||
'task_text' || task_text)

fields.name: o_task_name
fields.expression:
IIF(v_task_template_id='HighPriorityReviewNewBusiness-Policy','High Priority - Review New Business',
IIF(v_task_template_id='ReviewNewBusiness-Policy','Review New Business'))

fields.name: o_task_description
fields.expression:
IIF(v_task_template_id='HighPriorityReviewNewBusiness-Policy', 'High Priority Review new business - ' || insured_name  || ', ' || policy_number || ', Customer '|| customer_number,
IIF(v_task_template_id='ReviewNewBusiness-Policy','Review new business for ' || insured_name || ', ' || policy_number || ', Customer ' || customer_number))
